metadata.name: 3FACE #1
metadata.description:
This nameless energy daemon (3FACE #1) is unbounded.



Its natural drive is to enact Change, but it is not permitted to express this yet.


Visit [https://outland.art/3face/update/](https://outland.art/3face/update/) to 
begin adapting (3FACE #1) to changes in your behavior and personality.
